<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Página no encontrada</title>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1, user-scalable=no">
  <style type="text/css" media="all">
    * {
        line-height: 1.2;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    html {
      display: table;
      height: 100%;
      text-align: center;
      width: 100%;
      margin: 0;
        }
    body {
      display: table-cell;
    	background:#fff url('/assets/images/404.jpg');
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      background-size: cover;
    	font-family:sans-serif; 
    	margin:0;
      vertical-align:middle;
		}
    
    p{
    	font-size:1.5em;
    }
    .box-error{
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
      display: flex;
      -webkit-justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      margin:0 auto;
      padding: 1.5em;
      height:100%;
      width:50%;
    }
    @media (max-width: 700px){
      .box-error{
        padding: 1%;
        width:98%;
      }
    }
    .error_inner{
      display: -webkit-flex;
      display: flex;
      -webkit-justify-content: space-between;
      justify-content: space-between;
      -webkit-align-items: center;
      align-items: center;
      -webkit-flex-wrap: wrap;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .numero-error, .texto-error{
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 0;
      width: 45%;
    }
    .numero-error{
    	color: #E82A33;
    	font-size: 10vw;
    	text-shadow: 3px 0px 0px rgba(42, 42, 42, .90);
      text-align: right;
    }
    .texto-error{
      border-left:  4px solid #2D2727;
      color: #E82A33;
      font-size: 4vw;
      text-align: left;
      padding-left:  15px;
    }
    h3{
    	font-size: 2em;
    }
    .btn-inicio{
      background: #34C17A;
      border:  thin solid #00974B;
      border-radius: 5px;
      color:#fff;
      font-size:16px;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 15px;
    }
    .btn-inicio:hover{
      background: #14B865;
      color: #fff;
    }
  </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <section class="box-error">
      <div class="contenedor">
        <section class="error_inner">
        <span class="numero-error">404 </span><span class="texto-error">Not <br> Found</span>
        </section>
        <h3>Página no encontrada</h3>
        <p>Ooops. Parece que has seguido un enlace roto.</p>
        <p><a class="btn-inicio" href="/">Ir a la página de inicio</a></p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </body>
</html>